last_episode_to_air.name: The Grail
last_episode_to_air.overview: Rip infiltrates Quail's museum opening to steal the Holy Grail and bring Bella back to life, and Saltine goes on a risky mission to find out the truth about the coveted artifact.

name: Digman!
overview: Celebrity archaeologist Rip Digman and his team of experts travel dangerous parts of the world to unearth legendary artifacts and grow their reputations as fearless adventurers.

episodes.name: Pilot
episodes.overview: Washed-up archaeologist Rip Digman, trying to dig out of obscurity and redeem himself, recruits a sidekick to help him find the lost hat of Hammurabi, an ancient king of Babylon.

episodes.name: Et Tu
episodes.overview: Rip, Saltine, and Swooper travel to Venice to look for a historical batch of confetti, but find themselves embroiled in a mystery involving secret organizations, curses, gondoliers, and the knife Brutus used to kill Caesar.

episodes.name: Fear of GAWD
episodes.overview: When Rip accidentally destroys the Ten Commandments, humanity devolves into chaos, forcing Rip to hunt for the back-up set of commandments. Meanwhile, Quail Eegan’s new A.I. device gains sentience.

episodes.name: The Arky Gala
episodes.overview: Rip and Saltine attend the Arky Gala, the most glamorous event of the year, where Saltine makes an unlikely friend. But their reverie is shattered when the gala is taken hostage by a ragtag group of criminals.

episodes.name: The Mile High Club
episodes.overview: While searching for Amelia Earhart's plane, Rip and the gang find themselves taken aboard a floating airship in the sky, where Swooper finds a great new opportunity, Agatha finds romance, and Rip and Saltine find a lot of trouble.

episodes.name: Shakespeare's Lost Sonnet
episodes.overview: Rip goes on an undercover mission to find a long-lost sonnet from Shakespeare's legendary oeuvre, but things get sticky when he crosses paths with a charming thespian.

episodes.name: The Puff People
episodes.overview: Rip journeys to the distant Puffland in pursuit of the Holy Grail to resurrect his late wife Bella, but his solo mission goes awry when the king arranges for Rip to marry his daughter.

episodes.name: The Grail
episodes.overview: Rip infiltrates Quail's museum opening to steal the Holy Grail and bring Bella back to life, and Saltine goes on a risky mission to find out the truth about the coveted artifact.
